      "content": "okay that sounds intense... but honestly i've read online that some people take them together all the time without any issues. if i just take a smaller amount of juice or maybe just a little bit mixed in a smoothie, is that basically safe? i'm not looking to make huge lifestyle changes if it's not a life-or-death thing",
